title: 'Santa Claus Rally' Started Early, Dawson Says
description: Cameron Dawson of Newedge Wealth says the "Santa Claus Rally" seemed to start earlier this year, but they don't read much into it because it's just end of the year position chasing. She is on "Bloomberg Surveillance." (Source: Bloomberg)
